# 08.03 Revenue Model

## Overview

The Revenue Model defines how cmdOS generates sustainable income through its AI Execution Operating System ecosystem.

cmdOS is designed as a multi-layer business platform where revenue is generated from users, developers, businesses, enterprises, and ecosystem activity.

Core principle:

AI Infrastructure

↓

Products

↓

Services

↓

Marketplace

↓

Revenue

---

# 1. Revenue Model Purpose

The purpose of the Revenue Model is to define how cmdOS captures economic value from the platform.

It explains:

- Revenue sources
- Pricing structure
- Customer monetization
- Ecosystem economics
- Long-term sustainability

